=========================
= Generating Signed APK =
=========================
https://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/signed-apk-android

jdk bin folder - Navigate to that directory
-------------------------------------------
$ /usr/libexec/java_home

keytool command
---------------
sudo keytool -genkey -v -keystore zen-mobile-release-key.keystore -alias zen-mobile-key-alias -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000


==================================
= Build and Install unsigned APK =
==================================
Bundle your js:
$ react-native bundle --dev false --platform android --entry-file index.android.js --bundle-output ./android/app/build/intermediates/assets/debug/index.android.bundle --assets-dest ./android/app/build/intermediates/res/merged/debug

Create debug apk:
$ cd android/
$ ./gradlew assembleDebug

Then You can find your apk here:
$ cd app/build/outputs/apk/
